Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个~ 大人的C到底是怎样的啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烦死人了，才不做哩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.00,0:07:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿，来一下
