Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.28,0:08:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要搞Cosplay啊\N太过单调了吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说已经很够了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.08,0:08:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可不是一般的Cosplay\N这次的有加上一些料喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会让友纪有这个意愿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.52,0:08:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿，这张纸上面的台词\N就是追加的材料喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公老公~
